ent-RMCBackpackRTO = Радиотелефонный ранец ККМП
    .desc = Усиленный ранец, используемый для связи с центральным командованием. Обычно носится ОРТ.
ent-RMCBackpackRTOPMCBroken = broken We-Ya radio telephone pack
    .desc = A heavy-duty extended-pack, used for telecommunications between central command. Commonly carried by RTOs. This one bears the logo of Weston-Yamada and internal systems seem to be completely fried and broken.
ent-RMCBackpackRTOPMC = We-Ya radio telephone pack
    .desc = A heavy-duty extended-pack, used for telecommunications between central command. Commonly carried by RTOs. This one bears the logo of Weston-Yamada.
